Description:
Fantastic 2 Bedroom Rear Unit
Perfectly placed close to Dandenong High School and central Dandenong, this rear unit provides a low maintenance lifestyle that will appeal to occupiers as much as investors. Kept well throughout its short life the home sits at the back of a block of just 3 homes and features an open living/dining area and a neat kitchen with stainless steel oven and gas cook top. There are 2 bedrooms with built in wardrobes a well as a lovely bathroom with separate laundry and toilet. There's also ducted heating and a split system air conditioner for additional comfort and outside you find a single carport and a low maintenance courtyard with a shed and a covered patio for entertaining.

Description:
Endless Opportunities in Prime Location!
Located in the heart of Dandenong and on the famous red brick road is this lovely four-bedroom family home. Sitting opposite St Johns Secondary College, parks and only minutes to Dandenong Plaza, public transport and the Dandenong market. This sought-after area has seen capital growth of approx. 16.38% over the last 12 months (info from CoreLogic), we can assure you this home won't last long so be quick.
As you enter you are greeted with a light filled formal lounge that flows through into the meals area that is overlooked by the kitchen with plenty of cupboard space. There are four carpeted bedrooms on offer or three bedrooms plus a rumpus that are central to the main bathroom. Comprising of heating and cooling, professionally painted inside and out, as well as the roof and providing plenty of space for the whole family.
Step out to the great outdoors that features beautiful manicured gardens, a double tandem carport, a garden shed and an enclosed backyard for the kids to play in whilst the family enjoys a delicious BBQ under the pergola.
The 552m2 block has many uses and there is also the possibility to subdivide and build another home or knock the existing home down and build three brand new homes (STCA). Contact us today to avoid disappointment!

Walk to the iconic Dandenong Market and to the Plaza from this central and exceptionally secure townhouse on the edge of Dandenong's vibrant heart.

Description:
Say Goodbye to Body Corporate !!!
Closing Date Sale: Tuesday 15th-May @ 6pm (Unless Sold Prior)
Whether you're looking to downsize, get into the market or buy an investment property, this is where your search ends. With only 2 units on the block, say goodbye to Body Corporate.
Walk inside into an open living area and dinning with plush carpet. Equipped with a split sys-tem a/c and a wall heating unit. Walk through to a kitchen with 5 burner gas cooking, large stainless steel Westinghouse Oven/grill, double sink, plenty of cupboard and bench space with a window that looks out to your lush courtyard. Take comfort in your oversized master bedroom with walk-in robe and second bedroom with BIR and carpet throughout. Bathroom features both a shower and a spa bath with separate toilet. Generous size laundry with a back door leading to your private courtyard complete with lockup garden shed. All windows secured with roller shutters and an electric roller shutter for the sliding door.
Secured single garage with remote access with plenty of room in front for a second car if need be. Only minutes from everything Dandenong has to offer including Dandenong Plaza, Dan-denong Market, Dandenong Hospital, primary and secondary schools and plentiful public transport waiting to take you anywhere you desire. If you've been waiting for a property that is perfectly located and priced to sell, then this is it! An inspection is a must!

Description:
A 3 bedroom townhouse close to Dandenong Plaza
Tucked away from the road behind a small group of shops, this townhouse surprises with its privacy and low maintenance nature that will appeal to occupiers and investors alike. And despite its seclusion, the home is still within easy walking distance of Dandenong Plaza and market with buses, schools and trains also just minutes away. Behind a rendered front façade, you will find 2 living areas including a lounge room and a family/meals area incorporating the galley kitchen with electric oven and cook top. There are 3 robed bedrooms upstairs including the master with a full ensuite that complements the family bathroom and additional downstairs powder room. Ducted heating and a split system air conditioner add to the comfort while an alarm adds peace of mind. Outside there's a single garage with internal access and space in front to park another car plus a courtyard with covered patio and garden shed.

Description:
OUTSTANDING OPPORTUNITY WITH EXPONENTIAL POTENTIAL!!
LJ Hooker is proud to present this super rare and once in a lifetime opportunity in the heart of Dandenong. Sitting on approximately 2900m2 of prime soil, this property holds exponential future potential for development. Now is the time to take advantage of this goldmine and secure your long-term future.
This apartment complex is superbly maintained with outstanding tenants providing you with a stress free rental income of $210,000 approx per annum.
All 18 apartments are fully leased, each apartment offers two spacious bedrooms, one bathroom and one allocated carport. Each apartment is separately titled, providing you with the benefit to sell individually in the future.
Located across the road from Dandenong High School you are only within a short distance to Dandenong Plaza/Market, Dandenong Hospital, Chisholm Tafe, Dandenong North Primary School, freeway access, public transport, recreational facilities and all that Dandenong has to offer.
Call Ben Jusufi or Geoffrey Reis for any further information!
